EcoSim is a simulation application built in Python that aims to simulate ecosystems. Through randomized terrain generation, complex autonomous animal interactions, animal mutations, some user input, and a whole lot of coding magic, EcoSim truly has a life of its own. Let\'92s dive in and look at some of these features!\
